data.description: Welcome to the no-ferry island! This charming split-entry home provides all that Camano Island has to offer - only minutes away from public beaches, two State Parks, art galleries, eateries, and more! If you're looking to retreat to the privacy of Camano, then look no further. 3035 Sauk Drive boasts a beautiful, well-maintained yard with established fruit trees and vegetation. Inside you will find the space to make your dreams a reality. Upstairs there are two cozy bedrooms and an open-concept kitchen/living room with tons of natural light. Downstairs you will find privacy along with another bedroom, bathroom and spacious family room. If that's not enough, 3035 Sauk Drive also features a new 50-year roof, as well as a new front porch.
